      "title": "Operación diaria de aplicaciones Kubernetes",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Cuenta los pods que actualmente NO están en estado Running ni Succeeded dentro del namespace seleccionado. Uso operacional: este panel responde rápido si hay pods en fases problemáticas como Pending, Failed, Unknown o cualquier fase distinta de Running/Succeeded. Si muestra 0/OK en verde, no hay pods detenidos o pendientes según esta señal. Si sube a 1 o más, revisar la tabla 'Pods problemáticos actuales' para identificar cuáles son.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "index": 0,
                  "text": "OK"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "percentChangeColorMode": "standard",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(\n  kube_pod_status_phase{namespace=~\"$namespace\",phase!=\"Running\",phase!=\"Succeeded\"} == 1\n  unless on(namespace,pod)\n  kube_pod_owner{namespace=~\"$namespace\",owner_kind=\"Job\"}\n) or vector(0)",
          "format": "time_series",
          "range": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Pods no Running",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Cantidad total de reinicios de contenedores durante los últimos 15 minutos. Uso operacional: detecta inestabilidad reciente aunque el pod se vea Running ahora. Un valor mayor a 0 indica que algún contenedor reinició recientemente; revisar la tabla 'Contenedores con reinicios últimos 15m' y luego logs/eventos del pod afectado.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "index": 0,
                  "text": "OK"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "orange",
                "value": 1
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 5
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 6,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "percentChangeColorMode": "standard",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(increase(kube_pod_container_status_restarts_total{namespace=~\"$namespace\"}[15m])) or vector(0)",
          "format": "time_series",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Reinicios últimos 15m",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Cuenta los contenedores que actualmente están en estado CrashLoopBackOff. Uso operacional: esta es una señal fuerte de fallo de aplicación, configuración o dependencia. Si aparece en rojo, revisar primero la tabla 'Contenedores en CrashLoopBackOff' y luego logs, variables, secrets/configmaps, probes y dependencias externas.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "index": 0,
                  "text": "OK"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "percentChangeColorMode": "standard",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "sum(kube_pod_container_status_waiting_reason{namespace=~\"$namespace\",reason=\"CrashLoopBackOff\"} == 1) or vector(0)",
          "format": "time_series",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "CrashLoopBackOff",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Cuenta los pods cuya condición Ready está en false. Uso operacional: detecta workloads que existen, pero no están listos para recibir tráfico. Puede indicar problemas de readiness probe, dependencias internas, inicialización lenta o errores de aplicación. Si sube, revisar pods afectados y eventos del namespace.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "index": 0,
                  "text": "OK"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "none"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 18,
        "y": 1
      },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "percentChangeColorMode": "standard",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "showPercentChange": false,
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(\n  kube_pod_status_ready{\n    namespace=~\"$namespace\",\n    condition=\"false\"\n  } == 1\n  unless on(namespace,pod)\n  kube_pod_owner{\n    namespace=~\"$namespace\",\n    owner_kind=\"Job\"\n  }\n) or vector(0)",
          "format": "time_series",
          "hide": false,
          "range": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Pods no Ready",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Lista pods actualmente en fases problemáticas, excluyendo pods creados por Jobs/CronJobs para reducir ruido operacional. Uso operacional: si esta tabla tiene filas, revisar primero esos pods porque representan workloads vivos o controlados por Deployments/ReplicaSets/StatefulSets/DaemonSets que no están corriendo correctamente. Los Jobs fallidos deben verse en un panel separado.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            },
            "footer": {
              "reducers": []
            },
            "inspect": false
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {
          "countRows": false,
          "fields": "",
          "reducer": [
            "sum"
          ],
          "show": false
        },
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [
          {
            "desc": false,
            "displayName": "Time"
          }
        ]
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by(namespace, pod, phase) (\n  kube_pod_status_phase{\n    namespace=~\"$namespace\",\n    phase!=\"Running\",\n    phase!=\"Succeeded\"\n  } == 1\n)\nunless on(namespace, pod)\nkube_pod_owner{\n  namespace=~\"$namespace\",\n  owner_kind=\"Job\"\n}",
          "format": "table",
          "hide": false,
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Pods problemáticos actuales",
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Lista Jobs de Kubernetes con pods en fase Failed. Uso operacional: separa fallos de Jobs/CronJobs del monitoreo de workloads vivos para reducir ruido en la vista diaria. Si esta tabla tiene filas, revisar el Job/CronJob correspondiente, logs del pod fallido y eventos del namespace.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            },
            "footer": {
              "reducers": []
            },
            "inspect": false
          },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 0
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
        "y": 6
      },
      "id": 11,
      "options": {
        "cellHeight": "sm",
        "footer": {
          "countRows": false,
          "fields": "",
          "reducer": [
            "sum"
          ],
          "show": false
        },
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [
          {
            "desc": false,
            "displayName": "Time"
          }
        ]
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.3.1",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum by(namespace, owner_name) (\n  (\n    kube_pod_status_phase{\n      namespace=~\"$namespace\",\n      phase=\"Failed\"\n    } == 1\n  )\n  * on(namespace, pod) group_left(owner_name)\n  kube_pod_owner{\n    namespace=~\"$namespace\",\n    owner_kind=\"Job\"\n  }\n)",
          "format": "table",
          "hide": false,
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Jobs fallidos",
      "type": "table"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Muestra los contenedores que tuvieron reinicios durante los últimos 15 minutos. \n\nUso operacional: útil para encontrar pods inestables que quizá ya volvieron a Running. Si aparece una fila, revisar si el patrón coincide con despliegues recientes, OOMKilled, errores de startup, probes agresivas o fallos intermitentes.\n\nUn aumento sostenido puede indicar loops de crash, problemas de memoria (OOMKilled), fallos de startup o probes agresivas.\n",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": {
            "align": "auto",
            "cellOptions": {
              "type": "auto"
            },
            "footer": {
              "reducers": []
